DiagnosticOrderPriority

The clinical priority of a diagnostic order

This value set defines it's own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/diagnostic-order-priority

CodeDisplayDefinition
normalNormalThe order has no particular priority with it.
urgentUrgentThe order should be urgently.
statStatThe order is time-critical.

description.value: The clinical priority of a diagnostic order

definition.value: The order has no particular priority with it.
